title: Looking for a DUO partner within the next 30 minutes
body: I am in S5, looking to duo with someone, you have to know your shit, don't be absolutely terrible. However, that's a subjective statement. Write your IGN in the comments and whether or not you have skype. Also your age and the role and champs you play.

replies.body: I'm curious, why such short notice?
Using IE, have Skype, 99 years old, fiddlesticks jungle only.
